    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Following review of the structured credibility factor evidence, the assessment team determined that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to support the intended use. Several factors achieved levels below required thresholds; however, the team judged that compensating evidence from the Monte Carlo UQ study and the direct QoI relevance assessment provides adequate confidence in the model predictions for the VAD COU. The package is accepted subject to post-market surveillance commitments.",
